*lucene-1.4.3-r2 (14 Jul 2006)

  14 Jul 2006; Joshua Nichols <jnichols@gentoo.org> lucene-1.4.3.ebuild,
  +lucene-1.4.3-r2.ebuild:
  Revision bump to use new Java system.

  03 Mar 2006; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> lucene-1.4.3.ebuild:
  Quick fix to actually install docs under build/docs/.

*lucene-1.4.3 (25 Apr 2005)

  25 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> -lucene-1.3-r1.ebuild,
  -lucene-1.3.ebuild, +lucene-1.4.3.ebuild, -lucene-1.4.ebuild:
  new upstream version, fixes #90357. did some cleanup and introduced support
  for the source useflag

  03 Feb 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> lucene-1.4.1.ebuild:
  stable on amd64 and x86.

  26 Oct 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> lucene-1.4.1.ebuild:
  no longer use packed jars, #63281. Thanks too Jan Brinkmann
  <lucky@the-luckyduck.de>

  22 Oct 2004; Dylan Carlson <absinthe@gentoo.org> lucene-1.3-r1.ebuild,
  lucene-1.3.ebuild, lucene-1.4.1.ebuild, lucene-1.4.ebuild:
  Keywords ~amd64.

  16 Oct 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> lucene-1.3-r1.ebuild,
  lucene-1.3.ebuild, lucene-1.4.1.ebuild, lucene-1.4.ebuild:
  use java-pkg_dohtml instead of dohtml to also install the package-list in
  case of api docs: #50740

